[10.448983, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[90m‚Ēā\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m‚óÜ\u001b[39m  Which Expo (create-expo-app) template?\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m Default ‚ÄĒ Tabs + expo-router + TypeScript \u001b[2m(default)\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Recommended starter. File-based routing with bottom tabs, TS\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2mby default.)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBlank ‚ÄĒ minimal (JavaScript)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBlank ‚ÄĒ minimal (TypeScript)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mTabs (legacy)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBare workflow ‚ÄĒ no Expo modules\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[10.885915, "o", "\u001b[999D\u001b[9A\u001b[2B\u001b[J"]
[10.885972, "o", "\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mDefault ‚ÄĒ Tabs + expo-router + TypeScript \u001b[2m(default)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m Blank ‚ÄĒ minimal (JavaScript) \u001b[2m(Empty React Native app, no router, plain JS.)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBlank ‚ÄĒ minimal (TypeScript)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mTabs (legacy)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBare workflow ‚ÄĒ no Expo modules\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[11.05993, "o", "\u001b[999D\u001b[8A\u001b[2B\u001b[J\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m Default ‚ÄĒ Tabs + expo-router + TypeScript \u001b[2m(default)\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Recommended starter. File-based routing with bottom tabs, TS\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2mby default.)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBlank ‚ÄĒ minimal (JavaScript)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBlank ‚ÄĒ minimal (TypeScript)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mTabs (legacy)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óč\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBare workflow ‚ÄĒ no Expo modules\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m\r\n"]
