[11.369933, "o", "\u001b[?25h"]
[11.371736, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[36m‚óÜ\u001b[39m  Claude stack ‚ÄĒ D on wshobson / superpowers / pocock to customize:\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā ‚ĚĮ\u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m Karpathy CLAUDE.md guidelines\u001b[2m ‚Üí replaces CLAUDE.md\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[33m‚óź\u001b[39m \u001b[2mSuperpowers (TDD, debugging, brainstorming)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/skills/superpowers__* (flattened) +\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2m.claude/marketplaces/superpowers/ (mirror)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mclaude-mem (persistent memory across sessions)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí STACK.md (npx claude-mem install ‚ÄĒ user-scope)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mDefault subagents (code-reviewer, security-auditor, test-writer)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/agents/\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[33m‚óź\u001b[39m \u001b[2mwshobson/agents (80 plugins ‚ÄĒ 2 pre-checked as defaults)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/marketplaces/wshobson/ + flattened defaults in\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2m.claude/{agents,skills,commands}/\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mcc-lens (local analytics dashboard)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí STACK.md (npx cc-lens ‚ÄĒ user-scope)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2magentshield (security audit CLI)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/scripts/audit.sh\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mPretty statusline (tokens, rate limits, diff stats)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/statusline.sh + settings.json statusLine entry\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mocto-issue-tracker (GitHub issues triage skill)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/skills/octo-issue-tracker/SKILL.md\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mocto-scenario-tester (scenarios-before-code discipline)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/skills/scenario-tester/SKILL.md\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[33m‚óź\u001b[39m \u001b[2mMatt Pocock skills (21 skills ‚ÄĒ curated subset pre-checked)\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/skills/pocock__* (flattened)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā  \u001b[39m \u001b[32m‚óŹ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mAgent Teams (research preview, swarms) ‚ö† experimental\u001b[22m\u001b[2m ‚Üí .claude/settings.json (env entry)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[90m‚Ēā\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[90m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m  \u001b[2mspace toggle ¬∑ d details ¬∑ enter confirm ¬∑ esc cancel\u001b[22m"]
[11.960124, "o", "\r\n\u001b[?25h"]
[11.960174, "o", "\u001b[90m‚Ēā\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[33m‚Ė≤\u001b[39m  Agent Teams is a research preview. Requires Claude Code ‚Č•2.1.32, Opus 4.6+, and Pro/Max plan.\r\n"]
[11.960505, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[90m‚Ēā\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m‚óÜ\u001b[39m  MCP servers to configure (project-scope .mcp.json)?\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m GitHub ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ \u001b[2m(PR, issues, cross-repo code search ‚ÄĒ without leaving the terminal)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mContext7 ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Up-to-date docs for Next, Medusa, Prisma, etc. ‚ÄĒ no more hallucinated APIs)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mPlaywright (Microsoft) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Browser automation, tests UI, scraping JS, snapshots accessibility)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mPostgreSQL ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mSupabase ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mStripe (payments) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Charges, subscriptions, refunds ‚ÄĒ official agent toolkit)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mRevenueCat (IAP / subscriptions) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Mobile in-app purchases, subscribers, entitlements via v2 REST API)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBetter Auth (TS auth setup) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[12.219571, "o", "\u001b[999D\u001b[11A\u001b[2B\u001b[J\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mGitHub ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(PR, issues, cross-repo code search ‚ÄĒ without leaving the terminal)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m Context7 ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ \u001b[2m(Up-to-date docs for Next, Medusa, Prisma, etc. ‚ÄĒ no more hallucinated APIs)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mPlaywright (Microsoft) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Browser automation, tests UI, scraping JS, snapshots accessibility)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mPostgreSQL ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mSupabase ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mStripe (payments) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Charges, subscriptions, refunds ‚ÄĒ official agent toolkit)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mRevenueCat (IAP / subscriptions) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Mobile in-app purchases, subscribers, entitlements via v2 REST API)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mBetter Auth (TS auth setup) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚ĒĒ\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[12.25697, "o", "\u001b[999D\u001b[11A\u001b[3B\u001b[J\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mContext7 ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Up-to-date docs for Next, Medusa, Prisma, etc. ‚ÄĒ no more hallucinated APIs)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m Playwright (Microsoft) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ \u001b[2m(Browser automation, tests UI, scraping JS, snapshots accessibility)\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mPostgreSQL ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[2m‚óĽ\u001b[22m \u001b[2mSupabase ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[36m‚Ēā\u001b[39m  \u001b[32m‚óľ\u001b[39m \u001b[2mStripe (payments) ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ‚ėÖ\u001b[22m \u001b[2m(Charges, subscriptions, refunds ‚ÄĒ official agent toolkit)\u001b[22m\r\n"]
