[27.256512, "o", "\u001b[1G\u001b[0K\r\n4 \u001b[33m\u001b[1mmoderate\u001b[22m\u001b[39m severity vulnerabilities\r\n\r\nTo address all issues (including breaking changes), run:\r\n  npm audit fix --force\r\n\r\nRun `npm audit` for details.\r\n‚†č"]
